<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="least-adj">least <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /liːst/    美 /liːst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>最少的；最小的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He did <strong>the least</strong> housework in his family.
在家里他做的家务最少。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[强调几乎没有] 极微小的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He passed the exam with <strong>the least</strong> effort.
他毫不费力地通过了考试。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I haven't <strong>the least</strong> idea what you are talking about.
我根本不知道你在说什么。</p></div></div>